formalText: She states, "I guess it matters a little bit like he sort of makes me cry.".
She says, "I sort of just feel like a mess"
She agrees to feeling very frustrated about a couple things in her life.

She says "I just feel like I'm never quite there,
never quite able to do the thing that I really need to do"
She has not been cutting because
